<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">（愛知・西浦漁港）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">宮腰喜美夫・神奈川</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">油性ペン・固形水彩</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<citation>
<sentence>伊良湖から足助まで車で向かう途中、道に迷い出<sampling type="end" />会ったひっそりした漁港の風景。</sentence>
